description: Says Moo will repeat the onomatopoeia to your kids' delight.  In the future, we'll add more animals and even make a quiz out of it to teach your kids animal sounds.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Cow Says Moo what does the cow say
Alexa ask Cow Says Moo what the dog says
name: Cow Says Moo
shortDescription: An interactive version of the old classic, Cow Says Moo.  What does the cow say?
